{"tid":1630080,"cid":21,"subCid":3,"title":"【粵譯】《拔刀隊》","createTime":"2019-10-06T11:24:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-02T17:23:11.000Z","uid":69753,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3c8ea9ba4e7d4e22c4e70c52d92e6e2977412a44","tid":1630080,"uid":69753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:24:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/xAfaBrV-3qA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FxAfaBrV-3qA&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=cc484ff1\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/xAfaBrV-3qA</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">Invidious link: <a href=\"https://invidio.us/watch?v=xAfaBrV-3qA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finvidio.us%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DxAfaBrV-3qA&d=5qKB33MXKEG0NT2XrWEv6kXxRC0ARC%2FjKSdqd%2FiyNcw%3D&h=13ced593\" target=\"_blank\">https://invidio.us/watch?v=xAfaBrV-3qA</a><br />\n《拔刀隊》<br />\n我哋係官軍 我哋敵人係 天地不容嘅朝敵<br />\n敵人嘅大將係 古今無雙嘅英雄<br />\n跟隨其後嘅士兵係 慓悍决死嘅戰士<br />\n就算有不畏鬼神嘅勇氣 上天都唔會寬恕反骨仔<br />\n反叛者從古至今 冇一個成功嘅例子<br />\n敵方一日未全軍覆沒 我哋繼續前進再前進<br />\n拎出嗰把鋒利玉刀 帶住必死嘅覺悟衡衝向前<br />\n<br />\n喺皇國嘅傳統下 武士會有靈魂嘅加護<br />\n由維新廢棄咗嘅 日本刀喺呢刻<br />\n又要重演佢嘅榮譽 敵人又好我哋又好<br />\n一齊死於刀下 有大和魂嘅人呀<br />\n死就死喺呢一刻 唔好落後於人咁羞恥呀<br />\n敵方一日未全軍覆沒 我哋繼續前進再前進<br />\n拎出嗰把鋒利玉刀 帶住必死嘅覺悟衡向前</span>"},{"pid":"c224b5e41903bcacc7cabca7f00526437fc4598c","tid":1630080,"uid":299104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T11:26:08.000Z","msg":"講得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N2eJKVS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN2eJKVS.png&h=fd892c2e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GobPu5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGobPu5a.jpg&h=8c19a255&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/yYDlCk4w_-I\" data-